      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and never missed a service. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. You really won't find one in better condition. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
