    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to deliver a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally pristine, with a documented subframe inspection and factory-spec suspension geometry. Meticulously maintained with an exhaustive service history, this naturally aspirated masterpiece remains in its original, unmodified configuration, offering the precise turn-in and visceral feedback that defined an era of German engineering.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
