    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin still retains that new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing, while the dash and trim pieces remain in factory-fresh state with zero sun damage. Mechanically, the car is faultless. It comes with a comprehensive folder of every service record from the original dealership, documenting on-time oil changes and preventative maintenance. The engine runs whisper-quiet, the tires are fresh, and the transmission shifts with surgical precision. This sale includes both original keys, the factory window sticker, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. If you are looking for a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line, this is the one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
